HEADWORD: Madjoun
<hw>Mad"joun</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind., fr. Ar.
<ets>ma'j⟦umac⟧n</ets>.]</ety> <def>An intoxicating confection from the
